1. Who are we?
Petar Petrov and Asen Dimitrov, two independent game developers from Asenovgrad, Bulgaria
2. Contact Information?
Email:
pnamobilegames@gmail.com
3. What kind of personal information do we collect?
Our games do not collect any player data, however we use third party services, that collect data:
3.1. Services:
Chartboost –
https://answers.chartboost.com/en-us/articles/200780269
Fyber –
https://www.fyber.com/legal/privacy-policy/
AdColony –
http://www.adcolony.com/privacy-policy/
AppLovin –
https://www.applovin.com/privacy
Unity –
https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
Facebook –
https://www.facebook.com/legal/FB_Work_Privacy
4. What is the data being used for?
We use analytics data to better understand how our games perform for the users and how can we improve the games.
The ad companies and sdk’s use the data they collect to better tailor advertising to end users.
The social sdk’s are making it possible for the users to be able to share their moments to the social networks.
5. User Consent
By using our games, you consent to our privacy policy.
6. Contacting Us
If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy you may contact us here:
pnamobilegames@gmail.com
7. Changes to our Privacy Policy
If we change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page, and update the Privacy Policy modification date below.
